# Input

```md
[foo]: /url

[foo]: /url "title"

[foo]: /url 'title'

[foo]: /url (title)

[foo]: /url "title with spaces"

[Foo Bar]: /url

[foo]:
/url

[foo]: /long/url/path/to/resource

[foo]: https://example.com/very/long/path/to/some/deeply/nested/resource/that/goes/on/and/on/for/a/while

[foo]: /url "title"
[bar]: /url2 "title2"
[baz]: /url3

 [foo]: /url

  [foo]: /url

   [foo]: /url

[foo]: <https://example.com>

[foo]: /url "title"

Use [foo] in text.

[foo]: /url

[1]: /url

[long reference label here]: /url "title"

[foo]: /url ""

[foo]: /url "a"

[CapitalCase]: /url

[MiXeD CaSe]: /url

[foo bar]: /url "baz qux"

```


